Entry has recently been restricted to
a section of the cathedral that used
to be open to the general public.

rows.label: tlk46400071_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I feel like Acedia has started to
head down a worrying path ever
since the passing of Fan-sama...

rows.label: tlk46400071_03_msg0003
rows.name:
With the conflict between Superbia and
Invidia finally coming to an end,
shouldn't things get more peaceful?
